## Arithmetic Pipelines

\"Take my bank balance, subtract pending transactions, apply a 2% monthly interest, and tell me if I'll have more than $1000 at month's end.\"

Math pipeline into a comparison:

```scheme
(> (* (- (bank/balance) (bank/pending-total)) 1.02)
   1000)
```

*[needs: bank/balance, bank/pending-total]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire bank/* to Plaid or a CSV ledger -->

Three arithmetic operations, nested. No `balance-after-pending`. No `balance-with-interest`. Just close data, close paren.

