## Weighted Sum

\"Calculate my GPA: multiply each course grade by its credit hours, sum them, and divide by total credit hours.\"

```scheme
(let ((courses (academic/courses)))
  (/ (fold + 0 (map (lambda (c) (* (course/grade c) (course/credits c)))
                    courses))
     (fold + 0 (map course/credits courses))))
```

*[needs: academic/courses, course/grade, course/credits]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire academic/* and course/* to a transcript store -->

Two maps, two folds, one division. The entire GPA calculation is one `let` form.

