## Proportional Formatting

\"Tell me what percentage of my inbox is unread, rounded to the nearest integer.\"

```scheme
(let ((total (email/count-all))
      (unread (email/count-unread)))
  (if (= total 0)
      0
      (round (* (/ unread total) 100))))
```

*[needs: email/count-all, email/count-unread]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire email/* -->

