```

*[needs: todo/tasks]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire todo/* -->

Fetch, count, conditional word choice, concatenation. One `let` form.

---

## Elevation Change

\"Tell me if I've climbed more than 10 floors today.\"

```scheme
(> (fitness/floors-climbed-today) 10)
```

*[needs: fitness/floors-climbed-today]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire fitness/* -->

Fetch, compare. One expression.

