## Multi-Step String Build

\"Build a weather summary: 'Currently X°C and Y, high of Z°C expected'.\"

```scheme
(string-append \"Currently \"
               (number->string (weather/temperature))
               \"°C and \"
               (symbol->string (weather/condition))
               \", high of \"
               (number->string (weather/high-today))
               \"°C expected.\")
```

*[needs: weather/temperature, weather/condition, weather/high-today]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire weather/* -->

Three fetches, conversions, concatenation. One `string-append` form.

---

## Event Countdown

\"Tell me how many hours until my next calendar event.\"

```scheme
(let ((next-time (calendar/next-event-start \"primary\")))
  (/ (- next-time (clock/unix-time)) 3600))
```

*[needs: calendar/next-event-start, clock/unix-time]*  
<!-- BUILD: wire calendar/* and clock/unix-time -->

Fetch event time, fetch current time, subtract, convert seconds to hours. One `let` form.

