## Price Comparison

\"Tell me if the current price of a stock is higher than its 30-day average.\"

```scheme
(> (stock/price \"AAPL\")
   (/ (fold + 0 (stock/daily-close \"AAPL\" 30)) 30))
```

*[needs: stock/price, stock/daily-close]*  
